{"TopicId":132112,"ForumId":18,"TopicTitle":"The Martian Poll","CreatedByName":"Atlas2342","CreatedById":155194,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-14T22:47:28Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Atlas2342","CreatedById":155194,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-14T22:47:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWould you want a The Martian prequel, sequel, or nothing?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"davidy12","CreatedById":143411,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-14T22:50:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027d like a prequel with Ares I and II. NOT a sequel. I can\u0027t see how it would continue.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bill Phil","CreatedById":127797,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-14T23:33:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t think it needs a direct sequel/prequel. Another book in there same timeline, maybe with one or two recurring characters (old Whatney?).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stargate525","CreatedById":53585,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-15T01:45:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAndy Weir wrote a piece of flash fiction for popular science a few months ago; the first FTL test works, but accidentally sends the crew back in time. I want a novel based on THAT.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"FishInferno","CreatedById":106219,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-15T02:43:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222409479\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132112\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455500719\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002253585\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Stargate525\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n58 minutes ago, Stargate525 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAndy Weir wrote a piece of flash fiction for popular science a few months ago; the first FTL test works, but accidentally sends the crew back in time. I want a novel based on THAT.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNow that would be something.\u00A0 I think that The Martian is better alone, a prequel probably wouldn\u0027t be very interesting to non space geeks because nothing would really go wrong.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-02-15T02:44:55Z\u0022 title=\u002202/15/2016 02:44  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 15, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by FishInferno\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spaceception","CreatedById":152800,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-15T03:08:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027d like a prequel showing the Beginning of the Ares program, all the way to the Ares 3 launch.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Atlas2342","CreatedById":155194,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-15T08:25:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe we could have a sequel? Permanent base on mars, someting goes awry, crew has to get to defunct space station to get home. Maybe Jurassic Park francise style.....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-15T09:45:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSequel, as the main question is still unanswered: did they get married?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"YoetoJoe","CreatedById":126877,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-15T13:13:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI could see there being like a fact book with diagrams on how the spacecraft and surface infrastructure works but i dont want to see either a prequel\u00A0or a sequel.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-15T13:52:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s fantastic! The sequel is already \u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.amazon.com/The-Complete-Book-Potatoes-Gardener/dp/0881929999\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Epublished\u003C/a\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spaceception","CreatedById":152800,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-15T14:13:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222410303\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132112\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455544326\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n20 minutes ago, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s fantastic! The sequel is already \u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.amazon.com/The-Complete-Book-Potatoes-Gardener/dp/0881929999\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Epublished\u003C/a\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHa. Ha. Ha. \u003Cem\u003EVery \u003C/em\u003Efunny. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:wink:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Emperor of the Titan Squid","CreatedById":158183,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-24T20:56:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni say a prequel, talking about the beginning of the program.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222410001\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132112\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455529532\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 2/14/2016 at 4:45 AM, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSequel, as the main question is still unanswered: did they get married?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwho?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tex Mechs Robot","CreatedById":83406,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-24T21:59:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAndy Weir did say that he is writing another book unrelated to The Martian and it uses more traditional (unexplainable by actual\u00A0science) sci-fi technologies. I\u0027m looking forward to this!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/andy-weir-new-book_us_56731588e4b0648fe302a63c\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/andy-weir-new-book_us_56731588e4b0648fe302a63c\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spaceception","CreatedById":152800,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-24T22:07:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222599473\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132112\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221464123396\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022158183\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Emperor of the Titan Squid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Emperor of the Titan Squid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni say a prequel, talking about the beginning of the program.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwho?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMindy Park.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Andem","CreatedById":155578,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-24T22:29:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor once in my life, a sequel\u00A0about the first manned mission\u00A0to\u00A0Venus, and perhaps attempting to recover more data from Venera and the other Venus probes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222599563\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132112\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221464127657\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022152800\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Spaceception\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n21 minutes ago, Spaceception said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMindy Park.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat about Commander Lewis and her boyfriend?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spaceception","CreatedById":152800,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-25T01:30:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222599600\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132112\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221464128947\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022155578\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Andem\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, Andem said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor once in my life, a sequel\u00A0about the first manned mission\u00A0to\u00A0Venus, and perhaps attempting to recover more data from Venera and the other Venus probes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat about Commander Lewis and her boyfriend?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo that was her husband.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAt least, I\u0027m quite sure it\u0027s her husband.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-05-25T01:30:56Z\u0022 title=\u002205/25/2016 01:30  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EMay 25, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Spaceception\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-25T02:02:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222409924\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132112\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455524756\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022155194\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Atlas2342\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 2/14/2016 at 3:25 AM, Atlas2342 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe we could have a sequel? Permanent base on mars, someting goes awry, crew has to get to defunct space station to get home. Maybe Jurassic Park francise style.....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI would probably read this (and watch the movie) but nothing else. The story does not need or even suggest anything even remotely like a direct sequel.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Atlas2342","CreatedById":155194,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-25T02:07:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWait, he is writing another book? Set on the\u00A0moon?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n*internally screams*\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-25T02:25:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222599473\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132112\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221464123396\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022158183\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Emperor of the Titan Squid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, Emperor of the Titan Squid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222410001\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132112\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455529532\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 15.02.2016 at 0:45 PM, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSequel, as the main question is still unanswered: did they get married?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwho?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey.\u003Cbr\u003E\nWhy should we dictate them?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Robotengineer","CreatedById":104525,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-25T18:01:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222410001\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132112\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455529532\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn February 14, 2016 at 3:45 AM, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSequel, as the main question is still unanswered: did they get married?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSpace geeks care about that stuff?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}